    "description": "<strong>欢迎来到 Filthy Animals | 万圣节大劫掠</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/a280dcf02c07de0af1e6a2c22e7441e6.poster.avif?t=1651846598\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/a280dcf02c07de0af1e6a2c22e7441e6.webm?t=1651846598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/a280dcf02c07de0af1e6a2c22e7441e6.mp4?t=1651846598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>加入变种动物大军，在老大兼“肮脏动物拯救者”托尼的指挥下实施荒谬的劫掠.<br><br>在下水道里立足，在本地的超市开启肆无忌惮的万圣节大劫掠。抢夺现金，品尝玉米卷，燃放烟花，尽情地狂欢！<br><br>通过 Filthy Animals | 大劫掠模拟器，体验即将推出的精彩内容。在 2022 年推出的完整版游戏中加入动物大军，实施更大规模、更加疯狂和更有利可图的劫掠。<br><br><strong>特色： </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>基于物理学的谜题/战斗！<br></li><li>本地和在线*模式下可有 1 - 4 名玩家合作进行游戏！（*通过 Steam Remote Play 游戏）<br></li><li>采用 Active-Ragdoll 系统的玩家特征和 NPC！<br></li><li>极具 funky 色彩的原创音乐</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/17b39c9493b2b4d73cbe561eee00e7f0.poster.avif?t=1651846598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/17b39c9493b2b4d73cbe561eee00e7f0.webm?t=1651846598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/17b39c9493b2b4d73cbe561eee00e7f0.mp4?t=1651846598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Note:</strong> 注：本地多人和远程游戏需要手柄 - 推荐使用手柄<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764250/extras/cc8f5e6225e7385fa9915cfe4d52c9a4.poste